<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenue chez {{companyName}} - Votre partenaire financier de confiance</title>
    <style>
        /* Add some basic styling to make the email look better */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#212121">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <a href="{{CompanyLink}}" target="_blank">
                    <img src="{{templateCampaignImg}}" alt="{{companyName}} Logo" width="150" height="50"
                        border="0" style="border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="{{companyPrimaryColor}}">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px; background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, {{companyPrimaryColor}}, #2980b9);">
                <h1 style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                    Bienvenue chez {{companyName}}</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff; font-style: italic;">Nous sommes ravis de vous avoir à bord !</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#ffffff">
        <tr>
            <td align="center"
                style="padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #dddddd; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: bold;">En tant que client valorisé, vous pouvez
                    attendre un service exceptionnel, des conseils d'experts et des solutions financières innovantes adaptées à vos besoins.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666666;">Pour commencer, veuillez trouver ci-dessous vos informations de connexion :</p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><span
                            style="font-weight: bold;">Nom d'utilisateur :</span> {{username}}</li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><span
                            style="font-weight: bold;">Mot de passe :</span> {{name}}</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666666;">Si vous avez des questions ou besoin d'assistance, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter à <a href="mailto:{{CompanyLink}}"
                        style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"> {{CompanyLink}}</a> ou <a
                        href="tel:{{companyPhone}}" style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;">{{companyPhone}}</a>.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666666;">Vous pouvez également nous suivre sur les réseaux sociaux :</p>
                <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyLinkFb}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-facebook"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> Facebook</a></li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyLinkTwit}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-twitter"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> Twitter</a></li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyLinkInsta}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-instagram"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> Instagram</a></li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyLinkTiktok}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-tiktok"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> TikTok</a></li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyYoutube}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-youtube"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> YouTube</a></li>
                    <li style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;"><a href="{{companyPinterest}}" target="_blank"
                            style="color: {{companyPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"
                                aria-hidden="true"></i> Pinterest</a></li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#212121">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px;">
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">&copy;{{year}} - {{companyName}}. Tous droits réservés.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>